OL,3,CSenior minister to warn Labour to
OL,4,Cresist leftward shift after by-
OL,5,Celection loss
OL,7,FLabour should resist calls to shift
OL,8,Fleftwards in all areas of policy after
OL,9,Fits resounding defeat in the Gorton
OL,10,Fand Denton by-election, a senior
OL,11,Fminister will warn.
OL,13,FHome Secretary Shabana Mahmood is
OL,14,Fexpected to make the case for a new
OL,15,Fimmigration crackdown next week, at
OL,16,Fthe same time the Prime Minister faces
OL,17,Fintense pressure to shift his party to
OL,18,Fthe left or resign after the by-
OL,19,Felection loss.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
