OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1772240581
OL,3,CSenior minister to warn Labour to
OL,4,Cresist leftward shift after by-
OL,5,Celection loss
OL,7,FThe result of Thursday's poll saw
OL,8,FLabour come third behind Zack
OL,9,FPolanski's Greens and Nigel Farage's
OL,10,FReform UK in the previously rock-solid
OL,11,FGreater Manchester constituency.
OL,13,FBut a source close to the Home
OL,14,FSecretary told the Times: "The Labour
OL,15,FGovernment should not learn the wrong
OL,16,Flessons from its recent by-election
OL,17,Floss.
OL,19,F"The idea that we are losing Muslim
OL,20,Fvoters over immigration is just plain
OL,21,Fwrong.
OL,26,@vD@[OU{D@AOU
