OL,3,CSenior minister to warn Labour to
OL,4,Cresist leftward shift after by-
OL,5,Celection loss
OL,7,FIt comes after she has visited
OL,8,FDenmark, where a social democratic-led
OL,9,Fgovernment has drastically reduced the
OL,10,Fnumber of asylum applications to the
OL,11,Flowest number in 40 years and removed
OL,12,F95% of rejected asylum seekers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
