OL,3,CSenior minister to warn Labour to
OL,4,Cresist leftward shift after by-
OL,5,Celection loss
OL,7,FSir Keir Starmer on Friday
OL,8,Facknowledged it was a "disappointing"
OL,9,Fresult and that voters were
OL,10,F"frustrated", but insisted he would
OL,11,Fcarry on.
OL,13,FThe Prime Minister also pledged to
OL,14,F"fight against extremes in politics"
OL,15,Fon both the left and the right that
OL,16,Fthreatened to "tear our country apart".
OL,18,FHannah Spencer, a councillor and
OL,19,Fplumber, emerged victorious for the
OL,20,FGreens in Thursday's by-election with
OL,21,F14,980 votes ` a majority of 4,402.
