OL,3,CSenior minister to warn Labour to
OL,4,Cresist leftward shift after by-
OL,5,Celection loss
OL,7,FGreen leader Zack Polanski spent
OL,8,FFriday night on Channel 4's comedy
OL,9,Fchat show The Last Leg, where he was
OL,10,Fquizzed about the party's victory and
OL,11,Fvarious policy areas.
OL,13,FHe told the programme the Prime
OL,14,FMinister's framing of the Green Party
OL,15,Fpolicy on drugs as a blanket
OL,16,Flegalisation without any controls was
OL,17,F"ridiculous".
OL,19,FMr Polanski said: "There are drugs
OL,20,Fthat are dangerous, and those clearly
OL,21,Fneed to be regulated really carefully.
OL,26,@yD@AOUyD@LO]{D@SOU
