OL,3,CSenior minister to warn Labour to
OL,4,Cresist leftward shift after by-
OL,5,Celection loss
OL,7,F"On the other side of it, I'd say if
OL,8,Fsomeone wants a spliff: we are the
OL,9,FGreen Party. Let them get on with it."
OL,11,FThe Green leader later video-called
OL,12,Fhis new MP, Ms Spencer, during the
OL,13,Fshow, who watched on as he took part
OL,14,Fin a plastering challenge.
OL,16,FNew Gorton and Denton MP Ms Spencer
OL,17,Frecently took an intensive course in
OL,18,Fplastering, even as she campaigned for
OL,19,Fthe constituency, according to reports.
